('47', '03/06/2009 00:00', 'Barbara', '', 'B', 'Came primarily for a safe place and someone to listen. Thomas Dunn had suggested coming. He had been to LDHAS having arrived in the area to stay with a friend, but found his friend was staying in a B&B and so couldn''t offer shelter\nThomas is unemployed and homeless following a marriage breakdown, and possible health problems. Had slept rough the previous night on the steps of the Maguistrates Court House. Had little money, but had signed on at Job Centre for JSA and was looking for volunteering opportunities. Made phone call on his behalf for directions to Animal Care. Offered prayer, and tins for evening meal, also Life pamphlet, Gideon Bible and info on the Alpha Course', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
