('51', '', 'Kath', '', 'F', 'Telephone call- called primarily for food, her benefits have been stopped, and she lives on the Ridge Estate and feels unsafe. Her windows have been broken. Has 2 children currently residing with ex-partners mum. Offered food to her and told her she could come and collect it, and gave her CAP number', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('51', '27/07/2009 00:00', '', '', 'F', 'Came in today with her friend Elizabeth. She spoke about her situation. She is on the priority rehousing list because of harassment, including broken windows which she has experienced for 2 years plus. Gave CAP leaflet and emergency food parcel. Arranged appointment for her on Wed 29th. Alsio gave number for support with children 5-13, as Tara has 2 children, 4 and 7 years old.', 'C', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
