('53', '25/11/2010 00:00', 'Barbara', '', 'P', 'Collin called in to talk. H spoke about his drinking and epilepsy, his former marriage and his daughter- his desire to have reconcillation, to stop drinking ect.\nHe has been through a detox twice-The first while still mamed, second time when homeless for 18months. Both tries he began drinking as he came out.\nHe spoke about his conversation from Cof E to ortherdox. Hopes that in moving to Lancaster to live his life will be restored.\nKath and barbara prayed with before leaving. A listening ear and prayer', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
