('53', '04/02/2011 00:00', 'Gill', '', 'A', 'Colin called in for the first time since the "Bring a Tin" event.  Said then that he had been reducing his alcohol intake but since before Christmas he''d been drinking more again.  He''d fallen and banged his head badly.  Appears to be "stuck" with regard to his estranged wife - hoping to get back together.  Waiting to see his GP to be referred back to J2R.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('53', '15/02/2011 00:00', 'Chris', '', 'E', 'Colin called, he is reducing alcohol intake.  Looked clean and well.  Cleaned and tidied flat.  Said he had been praying and is now on a mission.  He prayed a prayer of thanks for the help he had received. We prayed for and encouraged him.  Pat had a picture which she shared.  He agreed that we could give his details to Home church in Morecambe.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
