('60', '24/09/2010 00:00', 'Gill', '', 'E', 'Jimmy called in, he wanted somewhere to sit in peace.  He is trying to cut down on his methadone and it''s not easy surrounded by some of the people in Lancaster.  He stayed for about one hour.  He is hoping to go to Victory Outreach in a couple of weeks and he wants \n\n\nto stay ''grounded''.  We prayed for hime to keep stable.  He seemed \nso much more quiet.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('60', '12/11/2010 00:00', 'Kath', '', 'E', 'Jamie came before we opened,we asked him to come back when we were open. He left his box and an l.p. Till he came back but he didn''t call back.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('60', '24/11/2010 00:00', 'Kath', '', 'F', 'Jamie has been thrown out of his squat, but has a new place with his friend Jay at skeron. Was in buoyant mood and asked for some food which a small amount was given.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
