('60', '03/07/2009 00:00', 'Barbara', '', 'M', 'Jimmy came in reporting despair- had recently climbed on the hospital roof, possibly suicidal? He had been admitted as an emergency on Wed by police, and sedated. His bike and bag with personal belongings ID and mothers photo was missing. Prayed for Jimmy, provided hospitality and offeref food and a tent which he did not accept. Made several phone calls on his behalf- CDT, CDT Support worker and his doctor. Arranged immediate \nappointment wiht his doctor,and accompanied Jimmy there.', 'O', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('60', '06/07/2009 00:00', 'Barbara', '', 'F', 'Given some, and update on his circumstances Jimmy asked for food', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('60', '10/07/2009 00:00', 'Barbara', '', 'E', 'Hospitality and update. Recieves his next payment Wed. His 2 art pens were stolen along with his other property- while his bag and photo were found by the police. He has seen someone else wearing his cap and jacket. He draws and reads before he sleeps each night, because drawing helps to calm his mind.\nHe has broken his relationship with his step father (mothers last partner) as he is a binge drinker. Jimmy finds it difficult living with him when he binges, and remembers him being violent with his sisters.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
