('64', '29/07/2010 00:00', 'Barbara', '', 'H', 'Ernest is homeless, newly returned to Lancaster. Already knows about Edward Street- suggested he goes there in the morning. As he \nis 69, Wesley House may be a possibility. Said he could not provide \nreferences, but asked about accomodation options in Morecambe.', 'E', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
