('65', '18/08/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', '', 'A', 'Received information that George was urinating in a public place as he was unable to walk to the nearest tiolet. Young teenage girls and people leaving play in the park had winessed this.  The informant, Terry Smith was concerned for George, his deteriating physical state and that it was witnessed.  He wanted us to contact L D H A S which I did and spoke to Gary the Centre Manager who said he will speake to George about this tomorrow.George had been unable to walk to the nearest tiolet.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('65', '19/08/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', '', 'A', 'Phoned L D H A S for update but unable to speake to Gary.  I will phone again on Monday.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
