('67', '21/12/2009 00:00', 'Kath', '', 'N', 'Located a sleeping bag from Mustard Seed, for collection tomorrow night. Jimmy offered him emergency sleeping bag for the night, also emergency food given.NFA, but not sure of reason- no addictions. No sleeping bag for tonight- has been relying on Christchurch Night shelter, but this was \nclosed due to misuse.\nRefferred to YMCA', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
