('71', '05/10/2009 00:00', 'Kath', '', 'D', 'Received referral from Jo at Help Direct for Mark and his wife Shandra. They are in the aftermath of a business collapse. They are concerned to know they are doing all they can. Phoned, but no answer\nLater, Kath phoned, but no answer. She contacted Help Direct to check she had correct number- and will continue to try 36773', '', 'H', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
