('73', '05/04/2010 00:00', '', '', 'P', 'Suggested speak to pastoral team and ask for prayer. Also to talk to her doctor. Offered and recieved prayer Pam reported feeling very depressed- more so than for a long time. She is seeing her psychiatrist at the end of the month. Unwilling to increase medication, or have CMN support, in case it ''stirs it up again''.\nFelt her husband did not understand her illness, and when he was depressed too it did not help her', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
