('75', '05/10/2009 00:00', 'Barbara', '', 'A', 'Came in with her mother- she was asking for help with addictions. She has been supported by CDT when she had been addicted to heroine. She self harms, uses alcohol and relationships\nRoot issues- late abortion while at Uni in Nottingham, and also the death of her father Rang Cedar House in Preston. If she can come in during the day, she will be made a priority- left a message with her sister with the number. Will look into places dealing with addiction/depression', 'O', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
