('76', '07/10/2009 00:00', 'Barbara', '', 'F', 'Spoke to Richard (Marie''s partner) on the phone and arranged for them to pick up an emergency food parcel from TOB on Fri 9th. Referred by Daniel Brown of Skerton Child and Family Support Centre Will refer to CCATS 01253 896444 for counselling due to depression as a result of recent divorce and mounting money problems. Have re-referred to CAP to help with mounting interest on providence loan and solicitors fees', 'C', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
