('113', '14/04/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Newly released from prison.  Homeless - does not want to go to LDHAS because wants to keep away from people with drug/alcohol issues.  Seeing a Disc worker tomorrow re accomm and band.  Wants to see more of his six year old son Barry - living with his sister.  Sister says he can see him monthly but David feels that is not enough.  Trying not to drink or smoke weed.  Keeps in contact football manager who is a Christian and contacted him while in prison - sent him Daily Bread and stamps.  He is providing two nights B&B.  Returning tomorrow for info re a caravan.', 'E', 'Prayed for him before he left.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
