('156', '29/11/2010 00:00', 'Barbara', '', 'F', 'Anneta asked for and recieved some emergency tins. Kath reinforced CAP guidelines re: seperate back account and paying money into that.\nShe mentioned her other son Sean staying and that she could not trust him.\n- Contacted The Olive Tree Ministries on her behalf for fridge\n- St.V + St.Pauls have one and will deliver next Wednesday', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
