('157', '09/08/2010 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Peter walked in after seeing the window display.  He is a believer but not in church at this time.  Gave up job for God.  Has spent seven years painting as worship.  He feels "bereft", tired and angry with God after leading people to Christ.  Has a family connection to Lancaster and keeps returning but his mother died before he could make contact.  He had a spiritual experience at 4, which helped him deal with abuse in the home.', 'P', 'Prayed for and suggested Christian counselling, church fellowship and healing of emotional wounds.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
