('162', '14/09/2010 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Ref from CMH nurse, unemployed and in debt', 'i', 'Unemployed and reliant on boyfriend and family for financial support, not in receipt of benefits due to a gap in her benefits due to an accident from 3 years ago? Debts are building up and Insurance company won''t pay premiums due to a pre-existent illness clause.  Been to Help direct and social prescribing attending confidence boosting course. Referred to CAP and CAB.  She felt rencouraged', 'C', 'O', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
