('165', '15/10/2010 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Called in to say thank you and to report progress. He has spoken to the new warden at Wesley House. A flat will be available soon and he will be back to see the manager.', 'i', 'He did not say whether he had completed an application. Gave him a TOB pack.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
