('189', '07/01/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Tracey came in with Nick Lumb. She''d been in hospital with a chest infection and was on medication.  She and Nick are homeless and were living in a squat. They asked for sleeping bags and a tent. 2 tents were supplied.They also received prayer for healing, change of circumstances and for accommodation.', 'T', 'Supplied 2 tents. Also prayer for an improved situation and healing.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
