('209', '17/03/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Phone referral from Lune Park Family Centre.  Worker to pick up emergency food for Tara and her two children.  Tara has mental health issues - will not leave the house.  Benefits suspended as right paper work was not sent in.  Has a partner that is around sometimes.  Has been caught shoplifting and finds it difficult to ask and admit she needs help.', 'F', 'Gave food.', '', 'L', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
