('211', '23/03/2011 00:00', 'Kath', 'Jacqui was referred to us by someone at Baptist Church. She has been in a rented house for 23years and has just been given notice as Landlord wants to sell property. She has been to Stategic housing and they have said that they will appoint a solicitor to fight to keep her home. The house needs a lot of refurbishment and she feels the time has come to move on.', 'H', 'Recommend that she asks her ''nice landlord'' if she can have a "rent holiday" to help her to save what is necessaryfor bond and deposit etc. Also gave her some student nos, to try and see if landlords have any houses.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('212', '25/03/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Sarah Jane''s mother phoned asking if we could help with food. Moving into flat, but waiting for community care grant to come through.', 'F', 'Reffered by Health Visitor, given bag of food and bread/milk.', '', 'O', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('213', '30/03/2011 00:00', 'Kath', 'Liz came in to bring some food for us - seen the message in the church bulletin.  As we talked it became obvious she had alcohol issues.  She is getting help from J2R and is hoping to do Celebrating Recovery at LFM.  Her boyfriend Michael has also had alcohol problems and has become a Christian.  She was very close to tears.', 'A', 'We invited her back to talk some more.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
