('218', '12/04/2011 00:00', 'Sylvia', 'Lyndon came in for the first time today to borrow some money for bus fare. He said he would return it tomorrow. He filled in the enquiry form and I gave him a welcome pack and had some time to sit with him and talk about the word for today. Lyndon read today''s quietly to himself and seemed interested.', 'O', 'We gave Lyndon ', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('219', '', '', 'New to area - from Ulverston.  Sam requested a sleeping bag but we didn''t have any - asked Edward St and they had one.  Will be at Edward St tomorrow.  Seemed quite out of it - on valium for depression and was tired because he slept rough last night.  Suggested he present himself at hospital if he didn''t feel much better soon - John Radcliffe took him to Christchurch for the night.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
