('229', '18/04/2011 00:00', 'Kath', 'TA for 3 months. David had seperated from his wife and 4 children approx 18 months ago due to his drink problem. There seems to be hope for reconcilliation if he can deal with this, which he seems willing to do. He has been to LDHAS and YMCA deposit scheme. He did intimate that he is very different (angry?) when drunk.', 'H', 'Suggested he visit Strategic Housing (not sure if he had done or where he was up to with this) as he has lived in the area all his life. We had a chat about God and he believes. I chatted to him about my testimony and invited him to church.He seemed quite open and said he would coome.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
