('232', '24/05/2011 00:00', 'Jenny', 'Someone from CAPS phoned on behalf of Leanne and her family (3 children - 7, 5 and 7 months) in need of emergency food.  Leanne does have a job but for some reason some benefits have been stopped and she only has Family Allowance to fall back on.  A family friend gave her a lift to collect 1 1/2 food packs and milk, bread and butter.', 'F', 'Chris rang Leanne on her mobile and told her to call in sometime in the afternoon.', '', 'O', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
