('235', '26/05/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Kelly called in - she is about to be evicted. The Social services had provided the bond etc for the property. The eviction has already gone throuhg to appeal and decision final. Her 16 yr old son Tyrone is living with her. Kelly asked if she could use our phone to contact landlords. Her bail conditions meant that she cannot access LDHAS.', 'H', 'She asked if it would be possible to work at TOB with LDHAS support worker. I phoned Gary manager of LDHAS on her behalf. He said he would see no objection but to bring it before LDHAS team meeting on Tuesday. Kelly said that she would come back tomorrow.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
