('236', '01/06/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Joint referral from Will Magowan (community Fire Safety and Health Practitioner 01524541685 and James Horton Community Police Support Officer) Raymond is a heavy alcohol and cannabis user. He has made a self referral to J2R- attended one, missed another. His parents both were alcoholics and died when he was 18. He was staying with his brother but had to move out when baby was born. His tent was slashed last night in Bolton le Sands. CPSO working with him.', 'F', 'Action: Emergency food, TOB welcome pack and relevant leaflets, toiletries, Tent and information re Morecombe Bay Credit Union.', '', 'O', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('236', '02/06/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'James Horton (PCSO7710) came in and brought a tent from Wilkinson''s for ', 'T', 'James had accompanied Raymond to strategic housing but Raymond was not in priority group. James wants to bring Raymonds case to special multi-agency group to be assigned special needs status.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
