('243', '24/06/2011 00:00', 'Kath', 'Son Jaiden (10 1/2) is sensitive and favoured by husband''s parents.  He''s been referred to Stepping Stones for anger management.  She is going through courts re contact of children - father is violent and alcoholic and only sees them on Sundays at the moment.  Court case 24th Aug - she is worried.  She works 3 days at hosp.  Lyn will ring when she feels she needs help.  May decide to take up counselling or just come and chat - take a day at a time.', 'i', 'KW to try and access some counselling.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
