('267', '22/11/2011 00:00', 'Jenny', 'Mark called in twice - 11.45am and 2.15pm.  First he called in to see Kath re his money problems i.e. Rent arrears at Longcroft.  He''s working hard - 12 hour shifts - and is looking at flats to rent.  Hasn''t had a drink for some time and is determined to keep his life on track.  Will call back next week when he has a week''s holiday.', 'D', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('267', '24/11/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Mark called in to say he is viewing a flat today in Morecambe''s West End.  Langley House have agreed to pay his bond.  His ex-partner has agreed that the children can visit him as soon as he is settled.  He needs the approval of his Probation Officer.', 'i', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
