('273', '25/08/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Karl asked for help with his debts.  He thinks he has an appointment with Hannah from CAP.  He spoke about his brother''s suicide earlier this year and how he would like to move back to Carnforth to be nearer his mother.  He has a long term drug problem and is now on methadone - would like to go to rehab at Littledale Hall.  He has been in work and would like to return.', 'D', 'Suggested he come back to talk to Kath.  Spoke about prayer - his uncle is a Christian and he used to play for Carnforth FC when his uncle was manager.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
