('274', '25/08/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Val was sent by CAP to see if we could help her with her electricity top-up.  She is in employment.  Spoke of her alcohol problems - seeing a J2R worker and hoping to do a home detox.  Her brother died a year ago from alcoholism and she is concerned she will do the same.  Started drinking during her divorce when her daughter was young.  She felt "bullied" over visiting rights.  She is also stressed due to work as a non-clinical auxillary.', 'O', 'Said we did not usually help in this way but would because she was referred from CAP.  Asked her to bring in receipt.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
