('298', '05/10/2011 00:00', 'Pam', 'Jan Knowles from Lune Park Children''s Centre rang - 382818 to refer Sarah and Michael Thompson and 2 children aged 3 years and 5 months. Sarah ahs been seriouslt ill and been hospitalised. She uses a wheelchair, condition is chronic and no improvement will occur. \nMichael is in work but has struggled to cope with his wife''s ilness, new baby and work. They are struggling financially and have recently been rehoused in Brookhouse. Referred to us for food parcel.\nMichael called in the afternoon to collect food.', 'F', '', '', 'O', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('298', '21/10/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Sarah phoned asking for help with food. Her husband, Michael, would pick it up.. Asked Michael in furture if he could make a referral through Lune Park Family Centre as we were establishing a more formal referral process. He said that hopefully they would not need help againg.', 'F', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
