('307', '16/11/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Alan came in to let us know what had happened.  He had been offered a job with Amazon in Edinburgh but had to turn it down as he is still unable to sell his flat in Lancaster.  He is trying to look at the blessings.  Reading self-help books and using the techniques.  Spoke about Jesus and God.', 'E', 'Offered and accepted prayer for wisdom and guidance.  Gave enquirer''s pack.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
