('307', '12/01/2012 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Called in to thank us. Decided not to attend the Scientist Church again. Has been interviewed for a job and bought a King James Bible. Spoke about faith, Jesus and God. Offered and received prayer for healing, eyes to see, favour, guidance, etc. Left encouraged.', 'P', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('307', '27/01/2012 00:00', 'Kath', 'Alan came to say he had lost his faith. His situation seems to be getting worse. He is getting deeper into debt witht the servic charge on his flat. He has been to CAB and they are helping him Barbara and I chatted to him and gave him some food and prayed with him.', 'F', 'Food', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('307', '09/02/2012 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Alan called in for a chat.  He has an interview on Monday.  Spoke of experience following prayer.  He went to the Priory and experienced a feeling of heat on his forehead.  Spoke about faith and experience.  He said he felt calmer since coming and does not react in the same ways to his problems.', 'E', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('307', '16/02/2012 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Alan came to give us an update.  Following the price reduction on his flat he has had a viewing and she is likely to put in an offer.  He has two more viewings.  He will hear the outcome of his interview when they have looked through all the applications.  He asked questions about faith and would like to attend an Alpha course.', 'E', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
