('312', '05/06/2013 00:00', 'Kath', '', 'O', 'On ESA but has had problems - has appealed twice - failed medical - missed app''nt due to attending funeral. Housing benefit ceased in relation to ESA cessation - arrears occured with rent. Got taken to court & ruled against him in his absence. Was told to sign onto JSA but ESA was re-instated but housing benefit arrears not paid. Has deteriorating heart condition , angina, & heart inflammation. Stress has caused his health to deteriorate & would like to apply for sheltered housing (over 60''s) but he is only 52 & needs supporting letter which KW will write on Friday. Coming in at 11.00 am on 7th june.', '', '', '1', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
