('316', '17/11/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Connie is struggling financially but not in debt.  She is a carer and has had to reduce her hours at work because of stress.  Recently supported a severely disabled person on weekend break.  Has just come out of a controlling relationship which ended in violence.  He tried to pour boiling water over her head - reported to police.  Her family do not live near to support her.  Feels depleted by friends who ask for help emotionally - feels has to protect herself now.  Came to Lancaster 11 years ago to rehab.  She has recently overcome gambling addiction.  Has a supportive doctor.  Connie is concerned her dog, Leila, is elderly and poorly.  She cannot afford further vet bills.  PDSA will not take her on because she is elderly.', 'O', 'Offered and received prayer.  Given Pathway to Peace and Travelling Light.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
