('316', '05/01/2012 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Connie came in before going to CAB.  At the beginning of the month she has no money left to live on after paying her bills - she showed us the printout of her bank statement.  She is on new antidepressants which make her feel unwell.  She is having troubles at work with her colleagues and has contacted her manager for more support.  She has enquired about a course called ''Love Self and Life'' to build up her confidence.  She has an appointment with the RSPCA for her dog.  Connie said she felt peace and encouraged to come back.', 'O', 'Given some emergency food - mainly soup.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
('316', '12/01/2012 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Has been signed off sick. Leila has had medication from RSPCA and Connie felt reassured. Given food, has been to Council to explain circumstances.', 'F', 'Food', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
