('327', '08/12/2011 00:00', 'Barbara', 'Phone referral from Maureen Cronin, Connexions, Morecambe. Reese came to collect food. She lived in Morecambe until 14 and  his family to Yorkshire (he is one of 7 brothers, 2 sisters and some step siblings). \n6 months ago he left Yorkshire where he had a job to return to Morecambe. He has stayed in several places incuding The New St Project on the high St and has been staying with his father. He liked the support he received at High St but not the behaviour of other residents.\nHe is on JSA, ideally looking for outside work in the construction industry. He has had some work experince and qualifications :- B Tec, GCSE''s, Maths, English, Science.', 'F', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'FALSE'),
